{"tid":974862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"違國歌法行為　警方可於犯法行為2年內追究","createTime":"2019-01-09T08:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T03:01:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"c4b7cda7576d1965cb22a92202e13575dea20960","tid":974862,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190109/s00001/f0238ff1bb26b7bd062e8510051e58a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2Ff0238ff1bb26b7bd062e8510051e58a3.jpg&h=f8df836c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局長聶德權今日稍後將舉行記者會，公布及解釋《國歌條例草案》細節。該局今午先向立法會政制事務委員會提交相關文件。<br />\n<br />\n文件指出，本港的《國歌條例草案》是參照2017年9月全國人大常委會通過的《中華人民共和國國歌法》（《國歌法》）而成。其中《國歌條例草案》第7條列明，任何人如公開及故意篡改國歌歌詞或曲譜，或以歪曲和貶損的方式奏唱國家，一經定罪，可監禁3年及處第5級罰款（即5萬元）。就以上罪行，警務處長可於發現或知悉有關罪行的日期之後一年內，又或當事人干犯該罪行的日期2年屆滿前，展開相關法律程序，以較早者為準。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國歌不得用於商業、私人喪事或公眾場所背景音樂，否則可處第5級罰款。<br />\n<br />\n草案亦指出，教育局長須向全港中小學發出指示，使學生學習歌唱國歌，和教育學生國歌的歷史及精神，和奏唱國歌的禮儀。草案另規定，包括立法會宣誓等官方儀式，國歌須以「符合其尊嚴的方式奏唱」，出席人士須「肅立和舉止莊重」，「並無不尊重國歌的行為」。<br />\n<br />\n上述條文並沒列明罰則，惟草案第11條列明，「在香港內觸犯有關國歌的規定的罪行，按照香港法律進行調查及予以檢控」，「如本條例與《國歌法》有不相符之處，本條例須解釋為《國歌法》的特別實施或改編本，並如此實施」。<br />\n<br />\n有關條例草案會在周五（11日）刊憲，本月23日即交立法會首讀及開始二讀辯論，此後恢復二讀辯論、委員會審議階段及三讀表決等程序，則待另行通知。"},{"pid":"d0b8881265f20059df6edde0c148e8d88e77fce1","tid":974862,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190109/s00001/1547020091067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2F1547020091067%2F&d=uIcbjDcYwpccDxCubFT6bzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=007ef452\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2F1547020091067%2F&h=a73ad538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190109/s00001/1547020091067/</a>"},{"pid":"13d10cdad57e2b09815029fad9b4d0f58376f611","tid":974862,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a300c2c92470b73db41d4cd73e6fd344a00ed61","tid":974862,"uid":91633,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab74cd730a7a2183851d49bf8e9d4f47f949ce7","tid":974862,"uid":25758,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"拍完片兩年後先放出黎又點"},{"pid":"be6473761fdc4016fa4af3d39446d5597d0308da","tid":974862,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"2ab74cd730a7a2183851d49bf8e9d4f47f949ce7","tid":974862,"uid":25758,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"拍完片兩年後先放出黎又點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"由放出當日開始計。"},{"pid":"fdecc71b7259b8d6172331f5ea1d479adb6811b2","tid":974862,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"2年太短<br />\n應該永久"},{"pid":"f00c9a519c349ff4ac46383d538a63b6ea122916","tid":974862,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be6473761fdc4016fa4af3d39446d5597d0308da","tid":974862,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"2ab74cd730a7a2183851d49bf8e9d4f47f949ce7","tid":974862,"uid":25758,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"拍完片兩年後先放出黎又點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"由放出當日開始計。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"但係案發時間係兩年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ab24e6564fa29764d122ae909e2ba5b8079489","tid":974862,"uid":42804,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"f00c9a519c349ff4ac46